sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Excel as Excel Spreadsheet
    participant AddIn as Excel Add-in Taskpane
    participant API as Next.js API (/api/excel-add-in/analyze)
    participant Cache as PostgreSQL (ResponseCache)
    participant Engine as Local Matching Engine (pipeline.ts)

    Excel ->> AddIn: User selects text column & clicks "Analyze Selection"
    activate AddIn
    AddIn ->> Excel: Read selected range values (Office.js API)
    Excel -->> AddIn: Returns texts array
    AddIn ->> API: POST { texts: string[] }
    activate API

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over API: Preprocessing Loop
        API ->> API: Compute SHA256 Hash for each row text
        API ->> Cache: Bulk query hashes to find cached results
        Cache -->> API: Return matching cache rows
    end

    alt Cache Hit (All Rows Found)
        Note over API: 100% Cache Efficiency
        API -->> AddIn: Returns sentiment & analysis columns
    else Cache Miss (Unique Pending Rows Exist)
        API ->> Engine: Run local classification on unique texts
        activate Engine
        Note over Engine: Local Leader-Clustering<br/>(Jaccard Character 3-Gram similarity)
        Engine ->> Engine: Select cluster representatives
        Engine ->> Engine: Run rule-based taxonomy parser
        Engine -->> API: Return enriched results
        deactivate Engine
        API ->> Cache: Bulk insert/upsert new entries (skipDuplicates)
        API -->> AddIn: Combine cache & fresh results and return
    end
    deactivate API

    AddIn ->> Excel: Write results matrix to adjacent columns (Sentiment, Theme, Category, Action, Urgency)
    AddIn ->> Excel: Apply visual formatting (color/bold cells)
    Excel -->> AddIn: Complete updates
    AddIn -->> Excel: Show "Complete! Sheet updated." status
    deactivate AddIn
